Packages 
Package Description
com.nokia.maps.common
The common package provides basic classes used by other packages in the JavaME Location API.
com.nokia.maps.component
The component package provides abstract base classes for creating custom MapComponents and custom EventListeners
com.nokia.maps.component.feedback
The feedback package provides a series ofcustom MapComponents which supply feedback to the user, either through offering a callback function to the MIDlet or updating the MapCanvas directly
com.nokia.maps.component.gesture
The gesture package offers a series of MapComponents which react to events generated by the Gesture API.
com.nokia.maps.component.touch
The touch package offers a framework for creating MapComponents which react to pointer touch events.
com.nokia.maps.component.touch.button
The button package provides abstract base classes to create touchable, visible buttons on the map.
com.nokia.maps.component.ui
The ui package contains a series of helper classes for rendering graphical elements onto the map.
com.nokia.maps.kml
The kml package provides classes to parse and render data from a KML file.
com.nokia.maps.kml.component
The component package provides kml components to render KML map objects and interact with KML features in the JavaME Location API.
com.nokia.maps.map
The map package provides classes that display an interactive map and allow you to create and add map content.
com.nokia.maps.routing
The routing package defines provides classes for route calculation.
com.nokia.maps.routing.enums
The enums package defines a series of constants for route calculation.
com.nokia.maps.search
The search package, has been deprecated.
com.nokia.maps.sharing
The sharing package provides classes for sharing a rendered map, location or place.
com.nokia.places
The places package provides data objects used to describe a place in detail.
com.nokia.places.geo.request
The request package provides classes used to make geocoding and reverse geocoding requests.
com.nokia.places.media
The media package provides classes to describe the data objects associated with an individual place, such as media images and reviews
com.nokia.places.media.request
The request package provides classes used to create requests to obtain media (such as images and reviews) associated with a specific place.
com.nokia.places.request
The request package provides classes used to create requests to the RESTful Places service.
